999827", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031547_1021011429333160_4176289926510597494_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=9lorZ79S0TQQ7kNvgFjVPx5&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAgWQtwMATe7kB64Ap0fhetjiJ1qIKQxiz99i7l9AVMoQ&oe=66F2A161"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 4.png", "id": "524012790104112", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001669_524012793437445_4891316513078544414_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=EPYmAtj9Nf8Q7kNvgGElu61&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBH4yHt5ZknJvGLgCwpqnQY_DnsQoXhAo2Nmp53JmyItw&oe=66F2B5DA"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 3.png", "id": "1187574142495669", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031470_1187574145829002_8495108821353233334_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=jIVhcvCTcCcQ7kNvgGirYHp&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA_pP3wNSIQyi_DrKt3FY0Ufe80du5l-iiWPZXG0-dwSQ&oe=66F2A870"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "38974450_2251639131854765_8396477208328520911_n.png", "id": "529809686395654", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476759_529809689728987_2021663405477506286_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xfkkpAkn04AQ7kNvgH1Gr_u&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAxWW2m9FUGF31MxCY61QBn7KK7eT1KPv_ROew50qfLHQ&oe=66F29A7F"}, "display_name": "Cellular Safari", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**Safari Cellular** is an innovative virtual reality app that turns learning about **cellular biology** into an exciting adventure. Designed for **students, educators and science enthusiasts**, this app allows you to explore an **animal cell in 3D** like never before. Through an immersive interface, you can navigate through different cell structures, such as **the nucleus, mitochondria, and endoplasmic reticulum**, discovering their functions and importance.\n\nEach component of the cell is represented in stunning detail, allowing you to observe and understand complex biological processes in a visually engaging way. **Integrated artificial intelligence** is at your disposal to answer any questions you may have while exploring, providing clear and detailed explanations.\n\nCellular Safari is not just a passive educational experience; it includes a series of **mini interactive games** designed to consolidate your knowledge in a fun and engaging way. Through **challenges and quizzes**, you can test your understanding of biological concepts, making learning an active and stimulating process.\n\nPerfect for use in education or as a self-study tool, Cellular Safari offers a new and innovative way to explore the microscopic world of the animal cell. With **high-quality graphics** and an **intuitive user experience**, this app turns the study of biology into an unforgettable adventure.", "short_description": "Discover the fascinating world of the animal cell with Cell Safari, the educational VR app that allows you to explore cell structures in 3D. Through interactive mini-games and advanced artificial intelligence, learn scientific concepts while having fun. Ideal for students and biology enthusiasts, this immersive experience makes learning an exciting adventure."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Landscape Mini.png", "id": "2930927027073306", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974477_2930927030406639_1033799740283778117_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hZ0rgDVX9gwQ7kNvgEueJi6&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBl4kaNJORLJzcWIuF7tiNyK87GVmf9Icrha-2_hAhodw&oe=66F2940E"}, {"file_name": "Hero Cover.png", "id": "1897915367381648", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75207242_1897915370714981_6546028005331927603_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4qt0XFi0bGEQ7kNvgH2cRvp&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAA_aVV0D1NUFWM1Q6UFKGrnDmHrO5tmioId1P2u7t6Pg&oe=66F28B4D"}, {"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "1156101178831306", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982713_1156101182164639_3284781712281521597_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=V-PsWyEYfTwQ7kNvgFhCv31&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYADGI-pZQ2tDJsjbDS49WUxwGPAAsWwEbS4pmJAQ6m6yg&oe=66F2914F"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "1035480321561334", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982526_1035480328228000_568917300582159945_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LOKVZvSmk4sQ7kNvgEpduS-&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAA2_pa2VPdEz7a3k_w-yXkBEZ9sOOpAE683ktMF2gV8Q&oe=66F2B3B8"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Portrait.png", "id": "840716281119571", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57574720_840716291119570_6338633741422904364_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=okfEiwSUA6MQ7kNvgFbOu68&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAarTto77Re433v9j-PLzQofK1lEQMTY2rzOVoOSmTkuA&oe=66F28E5B"}, {"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "488412717275961", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974525_488412720609294_7458364120634917665_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=U3s-b882ZrYQ7kNvgEI9rFu&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDs9y7f-0RCePO7sJrUhSZVfJOGrYD2q--JgvndChv9Fw&oe=66F2B7D1"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Square.png", "id": "427144199756021", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75223486_427144203089354_4369279694658394896_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3pBqyezy8JYQ7kNvgEm-asU&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDOJWNew6zzZen9BB6iyLj9Ohmem0m6Y5uuI1ugzMuTOQ&oe=66F2968F"}]}, "id": "520469743690183", "locale": "it_IT", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "Artboard 5.png", "id": "422140790868918", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031547_422140794202251_1640211663921085746_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Ucxm6wJJvDEQ7kNvgG7cg-I&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB2shyKVjivp3XIPsQje9uZOXdppd9-jbsKb6huUY2eLg&oe=66F29EAA"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 2.png", "id": "468838062692515", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984464_468838066025848_9209980070403449565_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=6kjqIGDlVtoQ7kNvgGDsGrd&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDp6Trn0gop2588M2QwjRXVwO2Fm7JIgBcuGSjKSBj9hg&oe=66F29A8C"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 4.png", "id": "481654227990009", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031353_481654234656675_3114596455803752280_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hYWSHTx6YscQ7kNvgELj5hX&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBoiZEcZI4aCxelLBGWQiPNDLiiBc-8_X_Q2mPRtTfh_Q&oe=66F29910"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 3.png", "id": "3889565187981667", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031547_3889565191315000_5528783709779854295_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=G-UCZnVDfjUQ7kNvgGIOwVh&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYALpsFu1JFhBTHm6TuDvUsqCFzZy18pUgqM_8Mosdusxg&oe=66F298A4"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 1.png", "id": "867384681933118", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003244_867384685266451_2340853765823917163_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3jeuZoBGSU0Q7kNvgEU8zDY&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB-rNG9TZ9qaDiJ-K4y0xY3mwCHavuK2h-t_r2loIiU5Q&oe=66F29CC5"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "38974450_2251639131854765_8396477208328520911_n.png", "id": "999991165259980", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476756_999991168593313_5483195490028886346_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=pMSTd6V3yWQQ7kNvgF2u5Z-&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBj7Uo4ZYFSlerEB3DTD3cpkevxiLwJwvKl1qcm5ML2dQ&oe=66F2AA31"}, "display_name": "Safari Cellulare", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**Safari Cellulare** \u00e8 un'applicazione di realt\u00e0 virtuale innovativa che trasforma l'apprendimento della **biologia cellulare** in un'avventura emozionante. Progettata per **studenti, educatori e appassionati di scienza**, questa app ti permette di esplorare una **cellula animale in 3D** come mai prima d'ora. Attraverso un'interfaccia immersiva, puoi navigare tra le diverse strutture cellulari, come **il nucleo, i mitocondri e il reticolo endoplasmatico**, scoprendone le funzioni e l'importanza.\n\nOgni componente della cellula \u00e8 rappresentato con dettagli straordinari, permettendoti di osservare e comprendere i processi biologici complessi in modo visivamente accattivante. **L'intelligenza artificiale integrata** \u00e8 a tua disposizione per rispondere a qualsiasi domanda tu possa avere durante l'esplorazione, fornendo spiegazioni chiare e dettagliate.\n\nSafari Cellulare non \u00e8 solo un'esperienza educativa passiva; include una serie di **mini giochi interattivi** progettati per consolidare le tue conoscenze in modo divertente e coinvolgente. Attraverso **sfide e quiz**, puoi mettere alla prova la tua comprensione dei concetti biologici, rendendo l'apprendimento un processo attivo e stimolante.\n\nPerfetta per l'uso in ambito educativo o come strumento di autoapprendimento, Safari Cellulare offre un modo nuovo e innovativo per esplorare il mondo microscopico della cellula animale. Con **grafica di alta qualit\u00e0** e un'**esperienza utente intuitiva**, questa app trasforma lo studio della biologia in un'avventura indimenticabile.", "short_description": "Scopri l'affascinante mondo della cellula animale con Safari Cellulare, l'app VR educativa che ti permette di esplorare le strutture cellulari in 3D. Attraverso mini giochi interattivi e un'intelligenza artificiale avanzata, apprendi concetti scientifici divertendoti. Ideale per studenti e appassionati di biologia, questa esperienza immersiva rende l'apprendimento un'avventura entusiasmante."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_na